dataIdInfo.idPurp: This layer provides an index map that can be used to locate individual scanned map sheets.
dataIdInfo.idAbs: This polygon shapefile is an index to 1:10,000 scale maps of Yokohama (Japan), titled 'Ichimanbun no ichi chikeizu Yokohama kinbō -- 一万分一地形圖横濱近傍/Ichimanbun no ichi chikeizu Yokohama kinbō.’To create this index, footprints were generated using the fishnet tool, and metadata were supplied for the digitized paper maps by Stanford University Libraries. After the footprints were created, the shapefile was trimmed and labeled according to the sources.
